Sentencas: Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.85Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-delta (BSCFN) perovskite oxides have been synthesized and studied as the cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: High performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-δ as cathode

Sentencas: XRD and SEM testing results demonstrate that BSCFN is chemical and physical compatible with La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta(LSGM) electrolyte.
Titulo: High performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-δ as cathode

Sentencas: The BSCFN cathodes exhibit excellent catalytic activity for oxygen reduction and mobility.
Titulo: High performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-δ as cathode

Sentencas: High maximum power densities of 0.22, 0.41 and 0.63 W cm(-2) have been obtained for the Ni-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-delta(GDC)/La0.4Ce0.6O2-delta(LDC)/LSGM/BSCFN electrolyte supported single cell at 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: High performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-δ as cathode

Sentencas: Further, the cell exhibits a stable performance under a constant current load of 0.6 A cm(-2) for over 100 h at 650 degrees C, indicating the BSCFN is an excellent cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: High performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.1Nb0.1O3-δ as cathode
